column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: CADBURY DAIRY MILK CHOCOLATE CARAMEL FUDGE SUPREME, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210497345
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK**, sugar, vegetable fats (palm, shea), cocoa butter, skimmed MILK powder, cocoa mass, WHEAT flour (with added calcium, iron, niacin and thiamin), reduced fat cocoa powder (1.5%), whey powder (from MILK), emulsifiers (SOYA lecithin, E442, E476, E471, sunflower lecithin), glucose syrup, invert sugar syrup, sweetened condensed MILK, tapioca starch, rapeseed oil, raising agents (E500, E503), salt, BUTTER, flavourings. **The equivalent of 426ml of fresh liquid milk in every 227g of milk chocolate.MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM, ACTUAL 23%.CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER. MAY CONTAIN NUTS. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 09/08/2017
